{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_06_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……雫ちゃんからメッセだ",
      "startTime": 2.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 841.1190074000001,
          "startTime": 2.8744523407
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "「すみれちゃんは凄く頑張ってくれてる\nでも、最近悩んでるみたいで心配」",
      "startTime": 8.7609670609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "「アイドルとしてはすみれちゃんの方が先輩だから\n相談しにくいかもしれない……けど」",
      "startTime": 17.4333331704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "「そんなこと気にしないで私にも頼ってほしい\n力になりたい。仲間として支えたい」……って",
      "startTime": 26.4637553617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど良かったじゃないか。雫はこのユニットに\n何が必要だと思っているのか、聞いてみればいい",
      "startTime": 35.6515603885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんな簡単に頼っちゃっていいんでしょうか\nセンターなら、もっとストイックに……",
      "startTime": 43.5999994556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "このユニットのコンセプト、覚えてるよな？",
      "startTime": 46.3282845935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　『みんなの素の魅力』で……あ！",
      "startTime": 49.5305139026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依の真似をするのが普段のすみれじゃないよな？\n言っただろ、すみれにはすみれのやり方があるって",
      "startTime": 57.8333327889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それに瑠依だって、一人だけでやってきた訳じゃない\n優も、すみれも、ずっと瑠依を支えてきただろう？",
      "startTime": 66.3080430051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……そうですね\nじゃあ今回は、雫ちゃんに甘えちゃおうと思います",
      "startTime": 74.3095402233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "と言うか、考えてみたら{user}さんにも\n沢山甘えちゃってました",
      "startTime": 82.3999997099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーは頼られるのが仕事だからな\n俺も、橋本さんも",
      "startTime": 87.5666663766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね！\nさとみさんとも、いっぱい話してみます！",
      "startTime": 91.5999997099,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7968.414767900001,
          "startTime": 99.5684144778
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.5497894409
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.5497894409
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "flowerstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7997894409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（――そして、橋本さんとすみれ達のユニットによる）\n（ライブイベントは、大成功に終わった）",
      "startTime": 99.6588942222,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9184.440891299999,
          "startTime": 108.8433351135
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 103.8398521228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "切りのいいところで上がるつもりが、もうこんな時間か\nん？　すみれからメッセージだ",
      "startTime": 109.7666663766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "「すずちゃんが酔っ払ったみたいに笑い続けてます」\n「あ、お酒は飲んでませんからね、当然です！！」",
      "startTime": 117.3630529828,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9793.6224476,
          "startTime": 127.1566754304
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（今は、ユニットのみんなで寮で打ち上げ中のはずだ）\n（凄い盛り上がってるみたいだな）",
      "startTime": 125.1666724801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "「こころちゃんが、なんだか凄く素直です」\n「録音して莉央さんに送りたいです……」",
      "startTime": 132.7333411813,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11585.6638594,
          "startTime": 144.3190050407
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "「それだけはやめておけ」……と、送信\nでも、こころが何を言ったのか気になるな……",
      "startTime": 141.1333411813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "「{user}さん、助けて下さい！」",
      "startTime": 145.3201091571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ！？",
      "startTime": 148.5592022541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 151.2567288918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみませ～ん……\nみんな、打ち上げしながらここで寝ちゃって……",
      "startTime": 155.5333391468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "私はすずちゃんの膝枕係に任命されまして\nそれは嬉しいんですけど、動けなくなっちゃって",
      "startTime": 164.7000180204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、平気そうな顔だったけど疲れてたんだな\nすみれは大丈夫なのか？",
      "startTime": 173.3666887561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "私はセンターですから\nみんなが安眠するまで、見届ける義務があるんです！",
      "startTime": 177.6666867215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、いつまで経ってもすみれが休めないだろう\n部屋まで連れて行こう。すみれも手伝ってくれないか？",
      "startTime": 185.4000190376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かりました！",
      "startTime": 189.3841895302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……\nなんとか、みんなをお部屋に帰せましたね",
      "startTime": 195.5000108996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "すみれも疲れてるのに、助かったよ\n寝ぼけてるすずを連れてくの、大変だっただろう",
      "startTime": 202.5105831808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、大丈夫です！",
      "startTime": 205.8401762366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばこの間、雫からメッセージをもらった後\nどんな話をしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 212.0333442329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、いろいろですけど……\n練習がダメだった日なんか、何度もメッセしちゃって",
      "startTime": 217.6000108996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_03-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "でも雫ちゃんはずっと相談に乗ってくれて\n頼れるお姉ちゃんみたいで、凄く嬉しかったです",
      "startTime": 226.2000027615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
